{"tid":1056433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"細路狗公園踩單車　管理員制止反被家長怒罵？","createTime":"2019-03-11T08:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T08:48:14.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5f39477c4cb30bdfd0e72e402aebf67a410b7b8d","tid":1056433,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T08:06:43.000Z","msg":"<strong>細路狗公園踩單車 管理員制止反被家長怒罵？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2VQUrVM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VQUrVM&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=be4aeb85\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2VQUrVM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190311/photo/bkn-20190311153421433-0311_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190311160107\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190311%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190311153421433-0311_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190311160107&h=b3f9b62a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解去寵物公園踩單車呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假日共聚天倫無可厚非，但也要選擇合適的地方。近日將軍澳有小朋友在寵物公園內踩單車，惟有管理員勸止時，家長卻反斥︰「我哋不嬲都係咁」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民周日（10日）在Facebook發貼指，有父母帶同2名小孩到環保大道寵物公園踩單車。當時現場有不少狗主正帶着愛犬散步遊玩，惟2名小朋友玩得興高采烈，又不時駕單車駛向狗狗。<br />\n<br />\n在場的管理員見狀曾出言提醒，但該對父母「大大聲鬧番人哋，仲好意思講『我哋不嬲都係咁』」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民直斥：「喺度踩單車，唔X係呀」、「有咩事畀狗咬到，肯定投訴點解狗公園會有狗」、「狗已經少地方玩，仲要霸X埋狗公園，仲要喺圍牆內玩」。"},{"pid":"a5bd1d98cfa9459ad55174a51f1651cd52ea9edb","tid":1056433,"uid":238551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25ca1ccc6e8b5646f0f0e3ccd5fe34bb3db603d6","tid":1056433,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5bd1d98cfa9459ad55174a51f1651cd52ea9edb","tid":1056433,"uid":238551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T08:13:47.000Z","msg":"支那人先係"},{"pid":"d6c19701277a24f5c308455d2dd3aec87d2e6b13","tid":1056433,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":